{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/networkmonitorsignalname\/notifynetworkmetered"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the network is considered metered."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Case","title":"NetworkMonitorSignalName.notifyNetworkMetered","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notifyNetworkMetered","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO24NetworkMonitorSignalNameO06notifyB7MeteredyA2CmF","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notifyNetworkMetered"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That is, whether the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"system has traffic flowing through the default connection that is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"subject to limitations set by service providers. For example, traffic"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"might be billed by the amount of data transmitted, or there might be a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"quota on the amount of traffic per month. This is typical with tethered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connections (3G and 4G) and in such situations, bandwidth intensive","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"applications may wish to avoid network activity where possible if it will"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"cost the user money or use up their limited quota. Anything more than a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"few hundreds of kilobytes of data usage per hour should be avoided without"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"asking permission from the user.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If more information is required about specific devices then the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"system network management API should be used instead (for example,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"NetworkManager or ConnMan)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If this information is not available then no networks will be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"marked as metered."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See also "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NetworkMonitor"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NetworkMonitorSignalName\/notifyNetworkMetered","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NetworkMonitorSignalName"]]},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/NetworkMonitorSignalName":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/networkmonitorsignalname","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NetworkMonitorSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NetworkMonitorSignalName","title":"NetworkMonitorSignalName","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"NetworkMonitorSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/NetworkMonitorSignalName/notifyNetworkMetered":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NetworkMonitorSignalName\/notifyNetworkMetered","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the network is considered metered."}],"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notifyNetworkMetered","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"NetworkMonitorSignalName.notifyNetworkMetered","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/networkmonitorsignalname\/notifynetworkmetered"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/NetworkMonitor":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/networkmonitor","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"NetworkMonitor","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GNetworkMonitor"},{"text":" provides an easy-to-use cross-platform API","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for monitoring network connectivity. On Linux, the available"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implementations are based on the kernel’s netlink interface and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on NetworkManager."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NetworkMonitor","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"NetworkMonitor","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"NetworkMonitor","kind":"symbol"}}}